Significant increase in the secretion of extracellular vesicles and antibiotics 
resistance from methicillin-resistant Staphylococcus aureus induced by 
ampicillin stress.

Kim SW(1), Seo JS(2), Park SB(3), Lee AR(1), Lee JS(1), Jung JW(1), Chun JH(1), 
