[Nursing Experience of a Child With Difficulty Breathing With End-Stage 
Niemann-Pick Disease Type C].

[Article in Chinese; Abstract available in Chinese from the publisher]

Chen YC(1), Chen SJ(2), Huang MC(3).

Author information:
